title: Jeremy & The Harlequins - American Dreamer (2015)
description:
I've been hoping to see a .FLAC version of this, but I haven't seen this released at all. These guys are amazing. I bought the album and now they are on tour and I will be driving 6 hours to catch them live. I hope by setting this album free, others will find out about them and buy their album and see them live.

My favorites are: This song has a brief snippet in Edge of Tomorrow, a 2014 Tom Cruise movie, how I first became interested in them.

They are kinda rockabilly malt shop ballads, IDK, define them for yourself.

Tracklist:

01 - Trip into the Light
02 - Heart of Stone
03 - Cam Girl
04 - Right out of Love
05 - Some Days
06 - Moonlight
07 - White Star Bright Love
08 - Settle Down
09 - You're My Halo
10 - Sunlight in the Rain

I didn't encode this. It varies from 249-293 kbps. BTW, popping my cherry with my first .torrent. Please seed if you love it and are able to
